OL,3,CSouthport vigil 'hardest challenge',
OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,FThe hospital chaplain who led a vigil
OL,7,Ffor victims of the Southport attack
OL,8,Fhas said supporting those affected by
OL,9,Fthe killings was "the hardest
OL,10,Fchallenge of my life".
OL,12,FThe Rev Martin Abrams was made an MBE
OL,13,Fat Windsor Castle on Wednesday 26
OL,14,FNovember, where he said he and the
OL,15,FPrincess Royal discussed "trying to
OL,16,Ffind the words when there are no
OL,17,Fwords".
