OL,3,CSouthport vigil 'hardest challenge',
OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,FMr Abrams supported the community
OL,7,Fafter the stabbings at a Taylor Swift-
OL,8,Fthemed dance class in Merseyside last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, Bebe King,
OL,12,Fsix, and Alice da Silva Aguiar, nine,
OL,13,Fwere murdered in the attack, and eight
OL,14,Fchildren and two adults were injured.
OL,16,FMr Abrams led a vigil for the
OL,17,FSouthport community and members of the
OL,18,Femergency services to pay tribute to
OL,19,Fthe young girls who were killed.
