OL,3,CSouthport vigil 'hardest challenge',
OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,FHe said receiving the honour was
OL,7,F"incredibly humbling", adding: "I'm
OL,8,Fquite numb, humbled. I think I just do
OL,9,Fmy job. For that to be recognised is
OL,10,Fvery special."
OL,12,FHe said the Princess Royal asked him
OL,13,Fabout the attack when she presented
OL,14,Fhim with his MBE.
OL,16,FMr Abrams said: "We discussed
OL,17,FSouthport. The vigil I led after the
OL,18,Fevents of July 29 last year, she was
OL,19,Fasking about how the town, the
OL,20,Ffamilies, how it felt to lead the
OL,21,Fvigil.
