OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,F"We talked about trying to find words
OL,7,Fwhen there are no words."/
OL,9,FAsked how it felt to support those
OL,10,Faffected by the attack, he replied:
OL,11,F"The hardest challenge of my life.
OL,13,F"I grew up in Southport, I work in
OL,14,FSouthport, I am part of in Southport,
OL,15,Fand for such a horrendous thing to
OL,16,Fhappen within our own community is
OL,17,Fjust awful.
