OL,3,CSouthport vigil 'hardest challenge',
OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,F"In Southport, we're defined by
OL,7,F(being) the town that has no sea,
OL,8,Fthat's what people think of when they
OL,9,Fthink of Southport.
OL,11,F"To be defined by something that is so
OL,12,Fhorrific is a tragedy."
OL,14,FMr Abrams, who was recognised in the
OL,15,FKing's Birthday Honours List for
OL,16,Fservices to the community in
OL,17,FMerseyside and West Lancashire, added
OL,18,Fthat being a hospital chaplain can
OL,19,Falso be "incredibly rewarding".
