OL,3,CSouthport vigil 'hardest challenge',
OL,4,Csays chaplain after MBE ceremony
OL,6,FHe said: "Sometimes people will ask
OL,7,Fhow I do what I do and I always
OL,8,Fanswer, 'If you can just bring, even
OL,9,Fto the most horrendous situations of
OL,10,Flife... a little a bit of hope and
OL,11,Fcomfort, that can be incredibly
OL,12,Frewarding, even in the midst of
OL,13,Fhorrendously sad situations'."
